Feature: Logging into Demo Web Shop Application

Scenario Outline: 
@ValidCredential
	Given user is in the Homepage
	When user clicks the Login
	Then user enters the Email
	Then user enters the Password
	Then user clicks the LogIN
	Then user Login is successfull
	
Scenario Outline: 
@InvaildCredential

Given user is in the Homepage
When user clicks the Login
Then user enters the InvalidEmail
Then user enters the InvaildPassword
Then user clicks the LogIN
Then user Login is Error Mesaage
Example:

|InvaildEmail|InvaildPassword|
|akash@gmail.com|Nittin@46|
|aknittin@gmail.com|